Roots: Our Journey Home

Biography Documentary hosted by Anderson Cooper, published by CNN in 2014 - English narration


Information
------------------------------

Storytelling is at the core of what CNN does, and in a week-long series beginning Sunday, October 12th, thirteen of the network's prominent hosts and anchors set out on a journey to find their ROOTS. These journalists embark on an emotional journey across continents as they discover never-before-known details of their family histories.
CNN anchors Anderson Cooper and Michaela Pereira will host a two hour special featuring 12 of the network's hosts and anchors stories. The special will also include interviews with Anderson Cooper, Michaela Pereira, Erin Burnett and Dr. Sanjay Gupta about what the experience has meant to them personally.

